Kill Audio v1 (2010) (digital) (d'argh-Empire)


KILL AUDIO follows the adventures of an immortal little troll who struggles to find a purpose in a land where musical and artistic creativity are controlled substances. With a growing team of misfits to keep him company on the crazy road to clarity and an aggravating nemesis setting them back at every turn, will Kill Audio ever find what he's looking for? Collecting all 6 issues of the fan-favorite series by the creator of THE AMORY WARS
